    Benchmarking ‘collections’

    benchmark.Rmd

    The goal of this document is to compare the performances of some of the existing packages.

    • dequer 2.0-1
    • datastructures 0.2.5
    • liqueueR 0.0.1
    • hash 2.2.6
    • hashmap 0.2.2
    library(microbenchmark)

    Queue

    microbenchmark(
    dequer = test_dequer_queue_push_pop(2000),
    datastructures = test_datastructures_queue_push_pop(2000),
    liqueueR = test_liqueueR_queue_push_pop(2000),
    collections = test_collections_queue_push_pop(2000),
    times = 10
)
    ## Unit: milliseconds
##            expr       min        lq      mean    median        uq
##          dequer  43.01679  46.67623  50.50658  49.06273  54.52528
##  datastructures 123.61592 126.62286 469.80624 132.01575 194.37339
##        liqueueR 258.74162 272.76595 299.10762 280.69855 301.28523
##     collections  28.75603  32.80052  39.74461  35.08216  44.54202
##         max neval
##    63.07655    10
##  3392.02348    10
##   444.22352    10
##    73.10002    10
